OL,3,CStaycations on the rise as British
OL,4,Cholidaymakers keen to avoid airport
OL,5,Cchaos
OL,7,FDriven by uncertainty surrounding
OL,8,Foverseas travel, British holidaymakers
OL,9,Fare increasingly opting for
OL,10,Fstaycations, ITV News Consumer Editor
OL,11,FChris Choi reports
OL,13,FThere is new evidence of a growing
OL,14,Fstaycation boom as holidaymakers are
OL,15,Fkeen to avoid airport delays and
OL,16,Ftravel disruption caused by the war in
OL,17,FIran.
OL,19,FBut as demand increases, there are
OL,20,Fsigns that prices are doing the same.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
