OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780128433
OL,3,CStaycations on the rise as British
OL,4,Cholidaymakers keen to avoid airport
OL,5,Cchaos
OL,7,FNew analysis by travel data experts
OL,8,FAirdna shows there was a 20% year on
OL,9,Fyear increase in average daily rates
OL,10,Ffor short-term rentals in Cornwall
OL,11,Flast month.
OL,13,FThere was a 14% rise in Chester, the
OL,14,FPeak District, and Scarborough, while
OL,15,Fthe increase was around 12% in the
OL,16,FScottish Highlands and 9% in West
OL,17,FWales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
