OL,3,CStaycations on the rise as British
OL,4,Cholidaymakers keen to avoid airport
OL,5,Cchaos
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe CEO of Butlins, Jon Hendry Pickup,
OL,13,Ftold ITV News bookings shot up as soon
OL,14,Fas trouble hit EU airports earlier
OL,15,Fthis year.
OL,17,F"This May, half-term term and late
OL,18,Fbookings were up 23% year on year
OL,19,Fcoming into May half-term," he said.
OL,20,F"So we're full this week, which is
OL,21,Fgreat."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
