OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780128433
OL,3,CStaycations on the rise as British
OL,4,Cholidaymakers keen to avoid airport
OL,5,Cchaos
OL,7,FIn sunny Bognor Regis, ITV News spoke
OL,8,Fto a mother who was happy to avoid
OL,9,Finternational travel this year.
OL,11,FTutu Onasamwo said: "The flights might
OL,12,Fbe really expensive, it could be hard
OL,13,Fgetting back, anything could happen
OL,14,Fand I don't want to be stuck abroad.
OL,16,F"I always do my holiday insurance, but
OL,17,Fyou just never know."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
