OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780128433
OL,3,CStaycations on the rise as British
OL,4,Cholidaymakers keen to avoid airport
OL,5,Cchaos
OL,7,FTravel advisor Emily Barnes says with
OL,8,Fthe rising prices of air travel, "it's
OL,9,Fjust been a lot easier and a lot
OL,10,Fcheaper to stay" in the country.
OL,12,FFor those looking to save money, she
OL,13,Frecommends "good caravan park", which
OL,14,Fare "more reasonable".
OL,16,F"People are looking closer to home and
OL,17,Frecognising that actually, there are
OL,18,Fsome amazing hidden gems," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
